# FILE: adminDashboard/userAccountManager/userAccountManager.desc
# ROLE: Supreme Authority & Verification Gatekeeper for All Account Types
# ROUTE: /admin/users
# ACCOUNT: Admin only
# THEME: Dark · high-density table · colored status pills · action buttons

## 1. VERIFICATION QUEUE (Students — Top Priority)
- HIGH-PRIORITY TABLE: bg-[#F43F5E]/5 · border-[#F43F5E]/20 top section
- COLUMNS: Student Name + UID · 📄 View ID Photo (modal) · Timestamp
- ACTIONS:
  - [✅ قبول]: sets isVerified: true → purple "موثّق" badge appears on student profile
  - [❌ رفض]: sets isVerified: false → triggers inbox notification to re-upload

## 2. BUSINESS ACCOUNT APPROVAL QUEUE
- Similar table for business accounts with status: 'pending'
- COLUMNS: Business Name · Business Type (vendor/advertiser/freelancer) · Contact · Submitted Date
- ACTIONS:
  - [✅ تفعيل]: sets status: 'active' → business can access /business dashboard
  - [❌ رفض]: sets status: 'rejected' → notifies applicant
  - [📝 طلب معلومات إضافية]: sends inbox message requesting more details

## 3. MASTER USER DIRECTORY
- SEARCHABLE + FILTERABLE grid of ALL registered users
- FILTER TABS: الكل · 🎓 طلاب · 💼 أعمال · 🔐 مشرفون
- COLUMNS:
  - Name + avatar
  - Account Type badge (colored)
  - Business Type (for business accounts): vendor/advertiser/freelancer
  - Status: 🟢 نشط · 🔴 محظور · 🕒 قيد المراجعة
  - XP Level (for students only)
  - Join Date
- WONDER FEATURE: "Shadow Login" — view the dashboard exactly as that user sees it
- ACTIONS per row: [👁️ عرض] [🧊 تجميد] [❌ حذف]

## 4. FINANCIAL & SUBSCRIPTION OVERSIGHT
- For student freelancers: subscription status + ShamCash transaction ID
- For business vendors: product listings count + revenue
- For business advertisers: active campaigns + expiry dates
- ACTION: [🧊 تجميد الحساب] — disables platform access instantly

## 5. XP MANUAL OVERRIDE (Students)
- Input: [+ / -] [Number] [Reason]
- Updates student XP instantly in the Growth Engine

## 6. BULK NOTIFICATIONS
- [📢 إرسال إشعار جماعي] — targets:
  - All Students · All Verified Students · All Business Accounts
  - All Freelancers (student + external) · Custom segment

## 7. ACTIVITY LOG (Bottom)
- "Admin verified student #9921."
- "Business account 'Elite Store' approved as vendor."
- "User #1042 reached Level 20."
